title: Season Five Battle Pass Trailer | Call of Duty®: Black Ops Cold War & Warzone™
author: Call of Duty
description:
If you want the upper hand, arm yourselves to the teeth. 

Gear up with the Season Five Battle Pass. Coming to #BlackOpsColdWar and #Warzone on August 12th at 9 PM PT.
